race.comment: DAMIEN (9) smart three-year-old gelded over the break. Sent to Queensland over the winter when raced without luck behind Brave Design and Autumn Boy at listed level. Given the two solid trials in readiness for this on the limit weight. Will prove hard to hold out. SHADY THINKER (5) classy Gawler-trained gelding who comes here second-up after stalking the fast tempo when a narrow winner over this trip at Morphettville. Rawiller goes on from the good gate and can make his mark in this harder contest. MIDNIGHT DYNAMITE (1) speared across in a messy run contest when running his rivals into the ground for a slick victory over 1300m at Randwick last Saturday. Clearly pleased the stable since, and he has a massive fitness edge over the bulk of these. Respect. TUNED (2) returns a gelding after racing without luck over the Queensland winter. Back in class and maps well with the two trials. Stays in the calculations. BARTOLF (4) deep into his prep and has claims in this harder contest.
